     <div class="container mtb">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                 <br>
                 <%=image_tag("sosjunglekids_children1.jpg",alt: "SOS Jungle Kids, India")%>
            </div>
            
            <div class="col-lg-6">
                <h4>Children in our school, Dhanwar</h4>
                <p>Today about one thousand students attend classes in kindergarten, elementary school or high school in Dhanwar.</p>
                <p>There is also a knitting training for village girls. Thanks to the support of foster parents in Belgium get students reading books, notebooks, pen, ink, pencils, a uniform, slippers, underwear, soap, toothpaste, extra clothing, ... and if necessary we will reimburse hospital costs.</p>
                <p>Many students live far from Dhanwar why most students stay in school. They get shelter with their own bed sheets and mosquito nets. Every day, the students 300 kilos of rice and 40 kilos Dahl (sauce for the rice). Most students are more comfortable at school than at home. No wonder some students who are not orphans, also spend their holidays at school.</p>
                
                
            </div>
        </div><! --/row -->
     </div><! --/container -->

